<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-46-0768 </DOCNO><TEXT>The applications of welding robots in vessel construction are reported.The pre-requisite system components and the technical means of installingwelding robots are shown by two practical examples. A main aspect isexact knowledge and consideration of allowed tolerances of componentparts. Task-tailored problem solutions have to be found on site, usingappropriate sensor techniques.</TEXT></DOC>